		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_QANAT_HELP">
			<Text>+1 [ICON_FOOD] Food for each Desert tile (but not oasis or Flood Plains) worked by this City. May only be built on or next to a Desert and next to a source of fresh water.</Text>
